                            <comment id="17264241" author="emilles" created="Wed, 13 Jan 2021 16:38:37 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Changes made for &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/GROOVY-9373&quot; title=&quot;ASM: rework line numbers for blocks with fast-path, try/catch or return statement insertion&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;GROOVY-9373&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;GROOVY-9373&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; in &lt;tt&gt;ReturnAdder&lt;/tt&gt; are the root cause.  &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/apache/groovy/pull/1443/files#diff-907636c890966e51907d123f089d830c5b99a9b440e462e69a0b49f891f7ec02&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://github.com/apache/groovy/pull/1443/files#diff-907636c890966e51907d123f089d830c5b99a9b440e462e69a0b49f891f7ec02&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The &lt;tt&gt;BreakStatement&lt;/tt&gt; is removed from the AST with the expectation that the remaining &lt;tt&gt;IfStatement&lt;/tt&gt; will return from each branch.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
